      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it is sound, with a smooth engine and responsive handling that makes for a comfortable driving experience. The exterior paint still holds a nice shine, though there are a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches expected for its age. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with all electronics and climate controls functioning as they should. It is a reliable, turn-key car ready for its next owner.",
