    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let this absolute gem go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car has been my pride and joy\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one and seriously looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s spotless inside and out, runs like a dream, and has been kept tucked away in a garage. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new and turns heads everywhere it goes, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
