      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example of the final naturally aspirated inline-six M-car. It features the S54 powerplant equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS, delivering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance: the rear subframe has been reinforced, the VANOS system bulletproofed with machined internal components, and rod bearings replaced with treated shells. The chassis retains its factory-spec structural integrity with refreshed bushings and OEM dampers. The exterior finish remains in showroom state with consistent paint depth and zero oxidation, while the Nappa leather interior shows no bolster wear or UV damage. A mechanically pristine, turn-key investment for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
