    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality masterpiece that has been meticulously maintained since day one. This vehicle boasts a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish, protected by a professional ceramic coating and free of any rock chips or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine, factory-fresh condition, featuring supple leather seating with no creases and a smoke-free environment. Every mechanical component has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with full documentation provided. Garage-kept and never driven in inclement weather, this car feels and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this is an unparalleled find.",
      "price": 48500.0,
