      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute showroom condition\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one and looks like it just rolled off the lot! Not a single scratch or dent to be found, and the interior still has that fresh, new-car smell. It drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
